  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>There are <strong><em>GoogleMap </em></strong>and <em>ComboBox </em>controls on the Form.<br />Use the ComboBox to select map control type.<br />See how the map control type is changing its appearance.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="1"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p><strong>GoogleMap.MapControlType</strong> property sets the type for the map control.<br />Property Type:&nbsp;Gizmox.WebGUI.Forms.Google.GoogleMapControlType.<br />DefaultValue - Gizmox.WebGUI.Forms.Google.GoogleMapControlType.<strong>SmallZoom</strong>.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>